{"tid":524775,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《戇鳩女權撚再度發功》上司凌晨發訊息祝生日快樂  女建築師稱私人時間遭侵擾","createTime":"2018-01-10T02:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T10:54:50.000Z","uid":34676,"like":90,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"728d60a8b5ed23ed96793b41575ce79469618287","tid":524775,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T02:53:35.000Z","msg":"放洋留學的女建築師投訴遭上司性騷擾案，申索人X指被告曾在凌晨發訊息祝她「生日快樂」，以及在佳節祝她「中秋節快樂」和「Merry Christmas」，認為對方侵擾其私人時間。惟辯方拿出被告手機紀錄，顯示X曾在農曆新年向被告發送「恭喜發財」的訊息，質疑是雙重標準，X否認並指每個人她均會發送，只是基於禮貌。<br />\n<br />\n任職建築師的申索人，控告利安顧問有限公司及公司董事黎啟繁，申索人於入稟狀稱 被告種種行為身心受創，索償41萬元， 並要求上司道歉<br />\n<br />\nX的投訴之一，是被告曾在2012年她生日當天的凌晨一時，發短訊祝賀她生日快樂。辯方質疑事實上X在當天早上11時才回覆，看來沒對X造成困擾，惟X指這是她的私人時間。辯方又質疑，按被告任何私人時間均不可接觸對方的標準，X在私人時間問被告妻子分娩情況，豈不是騷擾？X語帶激動反駁，「生BB係一生人一次，我生日年年都有，我都三十幾歲人，唔覺有咩出奇」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，X又投訴一次去內地工幹，要朝早乘港鐵到落馬洲。被告早上七時許向X表示身在上環港鐵站，問X會否同行。X感到「好驚」，指本來該程車想獨自前往，認為被告是故意要一同前行。辯方指被告居於西環，最近的港鐵站是上環，X表示她不知道。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180109/57686325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180109%2F57686325&d=wbybNbZG5TiC%2FlbXGPiTWJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=f906b735\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180109%2F57686325&h=14e6060f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180109/57686325</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你諗撚多咗喇，傻閪</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d3a59327fd04681fc3cc8cbfc0f7baf36821f1","tid":524775,"uid":77196,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T02:57:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">辯方指被告居於西環，最近的港鐵站是上環，X表示她不知道。 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三十歲人都唔知呢d野就死撚左去啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c126107d7f68cf7f6676cef13c48854709f32a","tid":524775,"uid":126648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T02:58:09.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"0efdf82ed323866a375d10c10d39bd6607721278","tid":524775,"uid":18735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T03:04:53.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪要冇男人搵先安樂"},{"pid":"22ad3ad19e70f6b334aaaae6e5efca453f55f8a1","tid":524775,"uid":31,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T03:05:51.000Z","msg":"屌 個男人唔受溝咪屈佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ba6c0685377f12212a365b3c488a7d2a623ecb","tid":524775,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T03:07:33.000Z","msg":"有冇咁傻閪 讀咁多書讀屎片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc66276557d52f335ddf744bf63bd1f133a3bba","tid":524775,"uid":738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T03:08:30.000Z","msg":"三十歲仲咁撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54bd248e322ca94111ef1e96156e7567aba1c609","tid":524775,"uid":116289,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T03:09:10.000Z","msg":"弱智都做到建築師"},{"pid":"f9deb359eb401b1678b7451e0b29c48f1e9cc6f4","tid":524775,"uid":148192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T03:13:27.000Z","msg":"比人祝福都嬲得落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大把人生日無人同佢講生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c952a09a80f7a8dfd38aa32574188a0eb519c9","tid":524775,"uid":45821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T03:14:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#metoo</span></span>"},{"pid":"ae43b9dbc7caa959f1fcb4f7bf83d22a2da23265","tid":524775,"uid":55597,"like":1